{
  "stem": "979.1",
  "chunk_idx": 13,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They told us-- I don't remember very clearly how we got there.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I mean, we decided that we go to this house, or to the other house.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But that was the district that we supposed to move, and leave all our stuff-- for instance, our piano, everything we had to leave.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They took the-- the Greeks, whoever went in the house, they took all our stuff.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Because then, there was a Greek woman, that-- she was coming.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "She was the photographer's wife.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Because we had in our backyard a photographer.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Because it was a tremendous backyard.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And we thought that, I mean, some were-- some anti-Semitics and so.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And we don't know who was anti-Semitic.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "There were good Greek-- Greek people too.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But when she saw that we were going to leave, all she wanted to know if she could get what we have.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we-- it hurt us.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Can I have this?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Can I have that?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And my father was so angry.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "He says, I'm going to break everything.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I'm not going to give everything.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "She said, my, this taste of feeling sorry for us, you know?",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But not all the Greeks-- and some Greeks were anti-Semitics, they were.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And-- but not-- some were really good, you know.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But when the Nazis-- when the Nazis came in, they didn't know who were the Jewish people.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "See, like, they say they can-- they can spot a Jewish person.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I say, they could not spot, because they think that Jewish have a special look or something.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They didn't know what they were.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
